21:05.198 --> 21:08.399
son of a bitch!
That is coconuts!

21:08.401 --> 21:09.934
I remember you!

21:16.375 --> 21:17.942
Do you miss spokesmodeling?

21:17.944 --> 21:19.777
Aye, I do a boat show
every now and then.

21:19.779 --> 21:21.545
That's how I keep
my hand in it.

21:21.547 --> 21:22.913
(Giggles)
Watch, watch.

21:22.915 --> 21:24.348
This is how
i sealed the deal.

21:28.754 --> 21:30.955
(Gasps)
That's you again!
